#shipsternbluff is regarded amongst the #surfing community as one of the #wildest and most dangerous locations in the world, both for the #surf and the prevalence of great #whiteshark. The #wave is also well known for its multi-faceted inner formations, referred to by many of its #surfers as steps, which give the wave a unique appearance and greatly adds to the challenge of surfing it.
